display_long_description:
Lumber Baboon is an open-world lumber simulation game where you take on the role of a woodcutter, starting from humble beginnings with nothing but a simple axe and a dream. Explore a vast, dynamic world filled with different types of trees, each with unique properties and values. Chop them down, haul the logs to your sawmill, and process them into valuable planks to sell for profit.

As you earn money, you can upgrade your tools, purchase powerful saws, and even invest in specialized vehicles to transport massive logs more efficiently. Expand your operations by purchasing land, setting up your own lumber mill, and automating your wood-cutting business. Discover hidden locations, rare trees, and secret upgrades that will give you an edge over the competition.

Trade with other players, form alliances, or compete to become the richest lumberjack in the world. Whether you're strategizing the best way to maximize your profits, exploring distant forests for the most valuable timber, or building your dream sawmill, Lumber Baboon offers endless possibilities for growth and adventure.
